before "p17 in"
key "Keeling2011"
literal "false"

\end_inset

 of a susceptible 
\begin_inset Formula $t_{i}p_{j}$
\end_inset

 recipient that encounters a 
\begin_inset Formula $t_{m}p_{n}\times t_{k}p_{\ell}$
\end_inset

 infected donor with chromosomal genotype 
\begin_inset Formula $t_{m}p_{n}$
\end_inset

 and plasmid genotype 
\begin_inset Formula $t_{k}p_{\ell}$
\end_inset

.
 Table 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
